{{Quote|This is Rogue Leader. There is one final refinement to our plans that you should know about. There is no system codenamed Phenaru. We're going back to Blackmoon. The mission as simulated was exact with the following exception&mdash;the simulated run through the asteroid belt to get into the planet was based on a run through the canyons on Borleias's sole moon.|[[Wedge Antilles/Legends|Wedge Antilles]], to [[Rogue Squadron/Legends|Rogue Squadron]]|<ref name="XW:RS">''[[X-Wing: Rogue Squadron]]''</ref>}}
'''Phenaru Prime''' was a fictitious [[Planet/Legends|planet]] created by [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] to disguise [[Second Battle of Borleias|attack]] on [[Borleias/Legends|Borleias]] and intended to throw off any [[Galactic Empire/Legends|imperial]] interceptions. It was created from Borleias, but added an [[Asteroid field/Legends|asteroid belt]] and different configuration of landmass and seas.

